name: Harshvardhan Tiwari
title: Founder & CEO
headline: Building Zynetic | Electrifying Parking Spaces | Collaborating with Real Estate Developers for building EV Charging Amenity.
organization_short_description:
Zynetic is a pioneering full-stack charging station operations and management company, with a significant presence in both India and Dubai. Established in 2022, we are dedicated to supporting the widespread adoption of electric vehicles (EVs) by providing robust and efficient charging infrastructure. Our comprehensive approach covers every aspect of EV charging station development, ensuring seamless integration and operation.

Our Services
Zynetic's full-stack operations encompass:

Identification of Suitable Property and Land for EV Chargers: We meticulously scout and evaluate potential sites, considering factors like accessibility, traffic flow, and proximity to key locations to ensure optimal placement.

Architectural Design: Our skilled architects design charging stations that are both functional and aesthetically pleasing, blending seamlessly with their surroundings while offering maximum convenience to EV users.

Civil Construction and Electrical Works: We handle all aspects of construction, from groundwork to the installation of electrical systems, ensuring each station is built to the highest standards and capable of withstanding heavy usage and extreme weather conditions.

Charging Station Management: Once a station is operational, we provide ongoing management and maintenance services, including performance monitoring, regular upkeep, and ensuring reliability and efficiency.

Zynetic is dedicated to driving the future of electric mobility by providing comprehensive and reliable charging solutions. Our presence in India and Dubai, combined with our full-stack approach to operations and management, positions us as a leader in the EV charging industry. As we continue to expand and innovate, we remain committed to supporting the transition to electric vehicles and contributing to a more sustainable future. For more information about our services or to explore partnership opportunities, please contact us. Together, we can power the future of transportation

Rich Technologies (RT), https://richtech.io, one of the fastest-growing IT software houses, is a people's company, and our motto is "code, develop and deliver with rich quality". Providing IT services at an international level, including but not limited to custom software and SaaS web application development, web design and development, mobile application development, marketplace development, creative designs, NFTs creation, and products for the metaverse. Welcome to Qanooni, the Legal AI Platform that works across all practice areas.  

Qanooni is a platform that was built by lawyers for lawyers, embedded completely within Word and Outlook. Our AI platform becomes personalized to your Style and Standards, supercharging you to complete end to end legal workflows in your way. Easy integrations with your firm's document management systems further enriches the system to allow you to tap into the firm's collective knowledge. Whether you are trying to create a draft, reviewing a document or searching for specific language, our legally trained AI system helps you to always achieve the best output you can create.

At Prabha Technologies, we are committed to leveraging our deep technical expertise and creative prowess to craft bespoke solutions tailored to meet the unique needs of each client. Our team of seasoned professionals combines passion with proficiency, ensuring unparalleled quality and efficiency in every project we undertake.

Whether enhancing customer engagement through immersive virtual experiences, optimizing operations with IoT-driven automation, or crafting intuitive mobile applications, our solutions are designed to elevate and empower businesses across diverse sectors.

name: Monica Perna
title: CEO & Founder
headline: Best English Coaching Provider 2022 by MEA Business Awards 🥇 | Outstanding Leadership Award 🏆 by Education 2.0
organization_short_description:
AUGE® INTERNATIONAL CONSULTING is a company providing education, training and consulting services. The company's core business is nourished by the sale of training paths held online and consulting activity.
The subjects dealt encompass English language, Information Technology, Management and Lean practices.
The company's customers are mainly represented by small and medium entrepreneurs, freelancers and consultants who want to optimize their business and expand it out of their native country. The company also serves private customers as well as big corporations who regularly ask for AUGE® International Consulting consultancy services.

AUGE® INTERNATIONAL CONSULTING è una società che fornisce servizi di istruzione, formazione e consulenza. Il core business dell'azienda è alimentato dalla vendita di percorsi formativi svolti online e dall'attività di consulenza.
Gli argomenti trattati comprendono lingua inglese e russa, informatica, gestione e pratiche Lean.
I clienti dell'azienda sono rappresentati principalmente da piccoli e medi imprenditori, liberi professionisti e consulenti che vogliono ottimizzare il proprio business ed espanderlo al di fuori del proprio paese di origine. L'azienda serve anche clienti privati e grandi aziende che richiedono regolarmente servizi di consulenza ad AUGE®.

AUGE® INTERNATIONAL CONSULTING - это компания, предоставляющая образовательные и консалтинговые услуги. Основной бизнес компании - продажа учебных курсов, проводимых в режиме онлайн, и консультационная деятельность.
 Охватываемые темы включают в себя: английский и русский языки, ИТ, менеджмент и методы бережливого производства.
 Клиенты компании в основном представлены малыми и средними предпринимателями, фрилансерами и консультантами, которые хотят оптимизировать свой бизнес и расширить его за пределами своей страны. Компания также обслуживает частных клиентов и крупные корпорации, которые регулярно обращаются за консультационными услугами в Auge® International Consulting.

organization_short_description:
At Myne, our passion is to significantly improve your financial well-being and ensure the protection of your wealth. Our platform is designed around four key pillars to assist you in tracking, managing, expanding, and safeguarding your assets.

We offer seamless connection to your financial life, integrating bank accounts, cryptocurrency wallets, stock exchanges, and enabling the addition of any asset type to provide a real-time view of your net worth. Additionally, we give a live view on your expenditures and access to a diverse investment marketplace.

Estate planning is also at the core of our services, we help you safeguard your wealth and secure your family's future. Myne gives you access to expert wealth planners that simplifies the process of drafting wills, establishing trusts, and more, making it all accessible through our user-friendly app.

Take the 1st step to your financial freedom with Myne.

organization_short_description:
Today, Payoll's is well on its way to deliver its mission of creating a frictionless digital ecosystem which allows businesses (large or small) to digitally - present their bills and collect their payments from customers (both domestic and overseas) through the customers preferred channel (whether that be their banking or NBFC apps, mobile or ewallets, payment kiosks or their neighborhood corner shop). 

Our ecosystem scale is rapidly growing and we have already connected over 20,000 businesses (service providers, billers) from across a 100 countries including 🇦🇪 , 🇮🇳 , 🇵🇰 , 🇪🇬 , 🇵🇭 , 🇿🇦, 🇬🇧 

Leading global and domestic banks, NBFCs, global e-commerce companies, wallets, marketplaces, telcos, and merchants (from multiple sectors) all form a part of the connected ecosystems and they leverage a number of products which all form a part of our overall platforms - PayollPay, PayollAccept, PayollKash, PayollXB, PayollDigitise and PayollAnalytics

Our goal is to accelerate the digital transformation of businesses with regards to their billing and payment collections.

name: Warren J.
title: CEO and Founder
headline: CEO and Founder of Pace Spedition | Transforming Global Logistics with Solutions Beyond Freight
organization_short_description:
As a freight forwarding company born in the Middle East and serving clients worldwide, Pace Spedition specialises in providing bespoke logistics solutions that drive global commerce forward.

At Pace Spedition, we take pride in managing the critical first and last mile of the supply chain with utmost dedication and precision. Our exceptional services are a result of our meticulously selected partners and our service-driven team. Furthermore, our state-of-the-art Pace Track System enables customers to have real-time visibility, control, and transparency throughout the entire logistics journey. 

We have tailored our services to address the varying needs of our clients. Our solutions encompass an extensive range of options, including air, sea, and surface transportation, customs brokerage, third-party logistics, projects and heavy lifts, aerospace logistics, fine arts logistics, automotive logistics, marine logistics, and retail logistics. 

Our commitment to excellence and innovation is unwavering, and we leverage our vast experience and expertise to deliver the best logistics solutions for our clients. If you are seeking a reliable partner to navigate the complex world of logistics, contact us today to learn more about how we can provide solutions that go far beyond freight.

To identify the highest value opportunities of your businesses and to address your most likely critical challenges, we assist organizations in providing the following services:

1.	Business Setup in Mainland (Dubai), Free Zone and Offshore;
2.	Bank account opening assistance;
3.	Facilitating Liaison with Government Officials & Business Community;

5.	Accounts and Bookkeeping 
6.	Tax Consultancy
7.	HR & Payroll 
8.	BPO Services
9.	Financial Consultancy – loans arrangements
10.	Audit and Assurance
11.	Business Advisory and risk compliance
12.	Immigration and document attestation services
13.	ESR, UBO & AML Compliance
14.	Company formation and PRO Services


Our main objective is to deliver highest level of quality services to our customers. We believe in maintaining a long-term and fruitful relationship with our clients by giving them utmost importance and care.

Looking forward to establishing a long term and fruitful relationship with you for all your business endeavors in the UAE.

Assuring you best of our services at all times.

Diagnio is a UAE Future 100 Company, with a mission to transform women's health diagnostics into easy to use, continuous, lab-accurate at-home experience. We help women get a clear understanding of their reproductive and hormonal health, be it diagnosing fertility issues, going through post-childbirth recovery, coping with unwanted endocrinological symptoms or navigating menopause.

Diagnio's first product uses a sample of saliva to measure estrogen levels to determine the cycle phase and ovulation via special medical device and mobile application. 

Pre-order now at https://diagnio.com with a 20% discount 🌿

The 3 key pillars of our offering are: objective data from biosensors, algorithms for personalized analytics and actionable advice from online consultations with specialists.

We have our own R&D capabilities, partnering Universities and patent-pending technology to develop our hormonal panel further.

name: Sergey Likharev
title: Founder and CEO
headline: Founder & CEO @ Waste-To-En | Sustainability enthusiast | Experienced C-suite executive in manufacturing, logistics, and supply chain management | PhD, MBA, CSCP, CLTD
organization_short_description:
Our purpose is to revolutionize waste management by efficiently converting municipal solid waste into valuable resources, mitigating environmental impact, and contributing to a sustainable future.

Our mission is to combat the daily dumping of 6 million tons of municipal solid waste, reducing land occupation, emissions, pollution, and landfill expansion.

Our vision is to use gasification technology to convert waste into synthesis gas, generating electricity and valuable products like industrial gases, fuels, lubricants, and chemicals.

Our goals are: to achieve eco-friendly waste management, protect the environment, and maximize resource utilization.

name: Emad Mansour
title: Founder & CEO
headline: Founder & CEO at Audacia Capital
organization_short_description:
Audacia Capital is a Dubai based investment bank with a primary focus on private equity and investment banking covering the Middle East North Africa and Turkey ("MENAT") region.

Licensed and regulated by the Dubai Financial Service Authority ("DFSA"), Audacia Capital's core activities in private equity and investment banking deliver exceptional, sustainable capital gains and fee-generated income that are aligned to Sharia principles.

Using deep knowledge of our primary investment markets and capitalizing on our unparalleled networks, we target privately held mature companies with high dividend yields, small and medium enterprises, start-ups and real estate opportunities. Using an astute investment model, we consider opportunities against defined and prudent criteria to identify risk-managed growth potential. We commit equity funding of ten to twenty percent to each private equity transaction while raising the remaining capital from co-investors on a deal-by-deal basis. 

Our firm capitalizes on its robust know-how of the MENAT region to amalgamate the interactions of committed and dedicated management teams of investee companies onto one platform. Moreover, Audacia Capital will channel its thorough expertise to formulate and implement innovative growth strategies to fulfill each organization's potential and maximize our shareholders' return on investment.

name: Bilal Kasih
title: Co-Founder / CEO
headline: Co-Founder / CEO, REVTON
organization_short_description:
Revton is the only eCommerce enabler in the Middle East and North Africa that caters to global retailers who are looking to expand and grow their presence in the region. 

With 20 years of experience in local and international supply-driven e-commerce, Revton deploys its expertise to support the entry of leading brands into the MENA market, enabling them to acquire and reach their customers directly through an end-to-end solution. From initial setup to ongoing optimization, first-mile to last-mile logistics, localization to customer support, Revton efficiently tailors its solutions to the brands' goals and handles every step of their expansion into the world's fastest-growing ecommerce region.  

At Revton, our local know-how and global vision enable us to fully localize your entire value-chain and to offer a speed to market solution that includes platform setup, IT integration, logistics, fully-managed operations, digital marketing, and superior customer service. For us, data-driven planning is the key to lay out a clear implementation and execution road-map that maximizes revenue.

With Revton's solution, entering the MENA region is nothing but a growth opportunity.

name: Martin Reynolds
title: Founder & CEO
headline: CEO @ Zero Carbon Ventures
organization_short_description:
We are a dynamic team of globally renowned multi-sector business and technology experts. Every member of the team is committed to bringing world-beating solutions to the United Arab Emirates and wider region to support high carbon producing companies transitioning to Net Zero. 

Zero Carbon's team scours the world to find innovations that can be nurtured, scaled up and deployed to create profitable and impactful propositions for the Middle East. 

We work with overseas researchers and start-ups specializing in carbon-reducing technologies, giving them investment, commercial know-how and vital connections to UAE companies that will immediately benefit from these innovations. 

In turn, our Middle Eastern partners are supported in rapidly accelerating transitions to lower carbon processes and creating carbon credits, often with no disruption to production or the need to make additional infrastructure investments. 

We invest, we educate, and we deliver.

name: Sophie Smith
title: Founder and CEO
headline: Founder and CEO at Nabta Health • Reimagining women's health in the Middle East & Africa
organization_short_description:
Nabta's pioneering hybrid healthcare model is built around women and families, delivering better outcomes and lower costs for everyone. We believe that health needs to encompass the ‘whole' of us and that we need a mind-body-spirit connection to bring out the happiest and healthiest versions of ourselves. 

Women's health in emerging markets remains underserved and under-researched.

By combining the best of digital and traditional healthcare, we empower women to detect, diagnose, and treat chronic diseases from home, by using specific health goals, and offering services which are both affordable and accessible. All our membership plans offer 24/7 hotline access, monthly walk-in clinics (where we also provide childcare for children under the age of 3, as we know how important it is to take some time for you!), the ability to download and access our App for ongoing goal setting, tracking and education, and of course, peace of mind that all services we offer are 100% confidential. 

✨ Transform your company with Nabta ✨

We offer a comprehensive solution to support your diverse workforce in new and compelling ways. Nabta are the leading platform for companies in the UAE who put their people first. We empower HR teams to offer accessible, inclusive, and personalised care for their people, and provide meaningful, quantitative improvements in health outcomes.

👩🏾 Woman-centric care: We use a holistic approach that offers multi-specialty to meet women's nutritional, mental and physical health needs.

📈 Improved outcomes: We have dedicated care coordinators and  a clinical care team, which is personalised according to women's age, stage, and goals.

💰 Fewer claims, lower costs: We know that proactive and continuous management supports early detection and diagnosis and reduces long term healthcare spend.

Want to learn more about our healthcare plans and the services we offer? Contact us today.

A Mind Cloud is what distinguishes a group of people, through its ideas, experiences, linguistics, behavioral patterns and final outcome. It answers questions like "How are we different from the rest?", "Why do we do what we do?", and "What do we want to achieve?".

name: Valentin Venetskiy
title: Chief Operating Officer and co-founder
headline: Chief Operating Officer and co-founder
organization_short_description:
Next'House is a Dubai-born hostel chain committed to redefining affordable luxury in the hospitality sector. With a portfolio of 178 beds across private and shared accommodations, we deliver exceptional comfort and style at accessible prices, catering primarily to millennials and Gen Z, including digital nomads, students, young entrepreneurs, remote workers and leisure travelers.

Our expert team has successfully launched and scaled Next'House over the past two years. As we set our sights on becoming the largest hostel chain in the MENA region, we aim to triple our number of beds by the end of 2025.

We are actively seeking new assets and opportunities to expand our footprint and continue providing top-tier experiences for our guests. Connect with us to explore potential collaborations and partnerships.

For more information, contact us at management@nexthousedxb.com.

name: Craig Fernandes
title: Co Founder/CEO
headline: CEO | Making higher education accessible & affordable |  Forbes 30U30 | $10.1M+ scholarships disbursed
organization_short_description:
SecureMyScholarship is a Dubai based edtech startup that aims to make higher education accessible and affordable for all students. Through our platform, we connect students with guaranteed scholarships and fee waivers at our partner universities. Our mission is to disburse $100 million in scholarships to students from working class and middle class families, and in the process change the lives of tens of thousands of people around the world. 

SecureMyScholarship, originally launched as a native platform on the Lock&Stock app in 2019, was born as a standalone brand with its own unique platform in November 2021. While our official headquarters is based in Dubai, UAE, our team is global, and the rockstars that are the heart and soul of our organization come from all over the world, including Dubai, India, Australia, Malaysia, Canada and Germany.

All universities listed on SecureMyScholarship provide students with guaranteed fee waivers and scholarships. As of June 2023, we have over 300 universities available on SecureMyScholarship, including 95% of all private universities in Dubai, over a hundred universities in both the US and UK, and many of the world's largest educational groups such as Navitas, Shorelight, Kaplan and Study Group. 

Aside from helping students secure scholarships for universities around the world, we also offer students end-to-end assistance, from course selection, university selection, application assistance, enrolment confirmation and visa assistance. We also work with third parties to assist students with accommodation and on-ground support once they arrive at their destination. Tens of thousands of students visit SecureMyScholarship.com every month from over 20 different countries.

As of July 2024, we have disbursed $9.1 million in scholarships to more than one thousand students.

At Kingpin, we are driven by the belief that there is untapped potential in wholesale and retail businesses. We consistently push ourselves to challenge how things are done to unlock new possibilities for growth.

We achieve this by leveraging technology to bring unparalleled speed, intelligence, trust and profitability. Everything we do, we do in a way that is intuitive, easy to use and impactful to the people that drive the business.

Kingpin gives you the power of full control on the levers of your business through a B2B SaaS solution bringing simplicity and scale how brands & distributors transact with their retailers.

Do you also believe your business has more potential? 

Let's get in touch.

headline: Founder & CEO | Proptech | Real Estate | Consulting | Real Estate Development | Hospitality | Joint-Ventures | Asset Management | Strategy | Board Member | Middle East | Africa
organization_short_description:
AIRE is comprised of AIRE Software and AIRE Consulting. 

AIRE Software uses big data, AI and automation to generate market-driven recommendations and ascertain the financial viability of real estate projects (residential, hotels, office and retail). 

AIRE Consulting provides customized consulting services to developers and investors across the Middle East & Africa.
 
What We Offer:
Our services range from detailed market research studies and bespoke financial modelling to location advisory and sustainability strategies. We also specialize in feasibility studies, highest & best use studies, master planning support and real estate portfolio optimization.
 
Our Expertise:
Our dedicated team excels in various sectors, including residential, hospitality, hotels, branded residences, office, retail, commercial, industrial & logistics, leisure & entertainment, healthcare, education and mixed-use developments. Whether you're exploring new opportunities or optimizing existing portfolios, we have the dedication and knowledge to help you succeed.
 
Why Choose AIRE Consulting:
•	Tailored Solutions: We understand that every project is unique. That's why we take a customized approach to deliver solutions that meet your specific goals and objectives.
•	Market Insight: With our in-depth market knowledge and research capabilities, we provide valuable insights to inform your real estate decisions and strategies.
•	Commitment to Excellence: At AIRE Consulting, we are committed to excellence in everything we do. From the quality of our work to the level of service we provide, we strive to exceed our clients' expectations.

organization_short_description:
About Globizera

We are driven by a bold vision: to revolutionize the way businesses and financial institutions interact, transact, and grow on a global scale. Our mission is to be your trusted partner throughout your financial journey, providing unparalleled access to capital, resources, and opportunities.


Our Vision:

We envision a world where businesses can thrive without boundaries. Our goal is to become the cornerstone of your financial success by offering a wide range of innovative solutions that empower you to achieve your goals.


Our Product Portfolio:

Receivable Financing: Unlock the value of your accounts receivable.
Export Factoring: Seamlessly navigate international trade.
Reverse Factoring: Strengthen your supply chain relationships.
CMA/Stock Warehouse Financing: Optimize your working capital.
Voyage/Shipment/BL Financing: Fuel your global shipping volumes.
Supply Chain Finance: Enhance your supply chain efficiency.
Vendor Finance: Support your suppliers for mutual growth.


What Sets Us Apart:

Global Reach: Our network spans across borders, connecting you with opportunities worldwide.
Customized Solutions: We tailor our financial products to fit your unique needs and aspirations.
Technology-Driven: We harness cutting-edge technology to simplify and expedite your financial transactions.


Our Funding Sources:

We collaborate with leading institutions, including banks, fund houses, and alternate finance providers, to ensure that you have the capital you need to thrive.


More Than Fintech - Your Strategic Partner:

Globozera Services is more than just another fintech company. We are your strategic partner in global financial solutions. With us, you unlock not just capital but also endless possibilities for growth and innovation.

headline: CEO | Insurtech | Digital Transformation | Leading Employee Benefits Innovator
organization_short_description:
IntelPeek was conceptualized and founded by a conglomeration of seasoned life insurance Executives who bring decades of credible hands-on experience in the insurance vertical with both local and multi-national corporations. it is designed to serve as an end-to-end unified platform encompassing the purpose-suited services for Insurers, Reinsurers and Distributors… all under the same umbrella.

Being the first and only life insurance focused platform in the GCC Region, this novel platform is The Go-To solution for all insurers and distributors having limited digital capabilities and know how. IntelPeek is a unique platform with deep routed expertise in life insurance products, distribution & administration.

IntelPeek can be best described as an orchestrator with digital solutions to liberate insurers and distributors to accelerate, scale innovation and be up to date with emerging technologies.

headline: CEO at Faze 3 | Project & Program Delivery | Digital Solutions | Training
organization_short_description:
At Faze 3 Consulting, we're dedicated to driving impactful change and innovation in the world of business. Established in Dubai in 2020, our journey began with a commitment to excellence and a passion for transforming organizations across diverse industries.

Drawing from our deep expertise in Program and Project Management, PMO outsourcing (PMO-as-a-Service), (E)PMO transformation, bespoke IT and digital training design and delivery, as well as digital and business transformation, we specialize in delivering strategic solutions tailored to meet the unique needs of our clients.

Our approach is simple yet effective: we prioritize innovation and efficiency to maximize the benefits for our clients. Whether you're seeking to optimize project management processes, enhance digital capabilities, or embark on a journey of digital transformation, Faze 3 Consulting is your trusted partner every step of the way.

With a team of seasoned professionals and a track record of success, we stand ready to help you navigate the complexities of today's business landscape and emerge stronger, more agile, and better equipped for the future. Experience the difference with Faze 3 Consulting – where innovation meets excellence, and your success is our priority.

OUR GOAL

Our approach is to continuously INNOVATE – our goal is to find optimum solutions and then leverage our industry experience to DELIVER successfully, at pace, for our clients.

OUR MISSION

Our mission at Faze 3 is to EMPOWER our clients to thrive in the digital age. 

OUR VISION

Our vision at Faze 3 is to be a catalyst for digital transformation and innovation. By fostering a culture of excellence, inclusivity, and sustainability, we envision a brighter, digitally empowered MENA.

Faze 3 Consulting is based in the United Arab Emirates and operating throughout the MENA region.

📞📧 Contact us on +971524123698 / info@faze3consulting.com

organization_short_description:
Equimost Management Services is founded by Mr. Milind Manohar Orpe, objectively to add economic and social values to corporates engaged in Marine, Shipping and Offshore drilling services.

Equimost Management Services help in creating synergies for its customers in Shipping, Oil and Gas sector, by bringing together business opportunity, industry experts and its Founder's experience over three decades of hands-on techno-commercial experience.

EquiMost has access to global network and expertise to support its customers objectively and provide tailored solutions in Drilling and Exploratory services, Shipping, Merger and Acquisitions, Marine Insurance, Maritime disputes, Claims, Rigs and Vessels sale and purchase,  conventional and alternative financing, Vessels and Rigs chartering, Heavy Lift transportation, New Build Construction Supervision, Drydocking, Repair Management, Statutory and Class Surveys etc.

EquiMost through its Advisory Partners offers consulting services on Ship Quality Assurance Programmes for time-chartered LNG, LPG carriers, Crude, Product tankers, and based on review of Historical data, Terminal feedback and Owner/Operator data, it draws strategies for successful outcome of SIRE and CDI inspections, Port State & Flag State inspections. Furthermore, EquiMost provide advisory services on Tanker and LNG/ LPG Vessels Vetting & Operator Audit processes, management of Incident Reports, Technical Holds and Terminal Holds including their review and closeouts.

name: Daryoush Golfar
title: Founder & CEO
headline: Founder & CEO - DARA HOMES Properties LLC/ Dubai Land Department Award Winner/ Motivational Speaker
organization_short_description:
DARA HOMES Properties L.L.C, based in Dubai, is a pioneering force in the real estate market, redefining industry standards for both employees and clients. Founded by an industry veteran - Mr. Daryoush Golfar, with over two decades of expertise garnered from esteemed organizations like DAMAC Properties, AZIZI Developments, and MAZAYA Holding, DARA HOMES is set to revolutionize the Dubai Real Estate Brokerage market.
With a proven track record of assisting thousands in finding their dream homes while collaborating with renowned developers, the founder has transitioned to the brokerage sector to introduce a fresh and innovative approach. At DARA HOMES, the cornerstone of success lies in considering employees as the most crucial asset. The commitment is to serve clients with unwavering honesty and professionalism, ensuring a completely new and exceptional real estate experience.
The organization fosters a culture where every employee is not just a team member but an integral part of the DARA HOMES family. The aim is to create an environment where individuals feel a sense of ownership and dedication towards the collective success of the organization.
DARA HOMES Properties L.L.C is poised to lead the way in transforming the Dubai real estate landscape with its commitment to integrity, professionalism, and a client-centric approach.
For further details and to explore the unparalleled offerings, visit the official website at www.darahomes.ae

name: Fawzi Hamze
title: CEO & Founder
headline: CEO & Founder
organization_short_description:
Assets Advisors Real Estate is a leading real estate firm headquartered in Dubai, UAE. Our team of experienced professionals specializes in sales, leasing, property management, and investment consultancy for both residential and commercial properties. We are dedicated to providing exceptional customer service, building long-term relationships with clients, and delivering results in the highly competitive UAE real estate market.

Our founder, Fawzi Hamze, is an experienced real estate entrepreneur with over 8 years of experience in the Dubai real estate market. Fawzi has worked with EMAAR, the third-largest developer in the world, and the largest developer in the world outside the China market. He is an innovative leader in the UAE market and has established a reputation for expertise and excellence in the dynamic real estate market.

At Assets Advisors Real Estate, we believe in transparency, integrity, and honesty, and we pride ourselves on providing clients with a personalized and professional experience. We work with our clients to help them achieve their real estate goals and build strong portfolios. Our recent recognition by EMAAR for outstanding sales performance serves as a testament to our commitment to excellence and delivering results for our clients.

In addition to traditional real estate services, we also collaborate with partners to hand-pick the very best assets from around the world, including luxury yachts and private jets, to provide our clients with diversified and comprehensive asset portfolios.
If you're looking for a trusted and reputable real estate partner in Dubai or the UAE, Assets Advisors Real Estate is the right choice. Contact us to learn more about our services and how we can help you achieve your real estate goals.

organization_short_description:
Welcome to talentX 🚀, the Middle East's leading People & Culture Experience Consultancy, dedicated to helping organizations build high-performance teams where talent thrives. From our hubs in Dubai and Riyadh, we're on a mission to unlock potential and drive success through our core mantra: Hire, Inspire, and Win! 🏆

We partner with founders, CEOs, and leaders to create tailored people solutions that deliver real impact, including:

- Culture Design & Activation
- Employer Branding & EVP Development
- Leadership Development
- Gamified & Immersive L&D Programs
- Performance Improvement Strategies
- People Experience Design
- Strategic Talent Acquisition

Powered by our People Science team, we blend cutting-edge organizational psychology with data science to:

- Build thriving, high-energy cultures
- Enhance employee experiences
- Drive high performance and innovation
- Attract and retain top talent

In the diverse business landscape of the Middle East 🌍, we transform cultural diversity into a competitive advantage. Our approach combines local insights with global expertise and excellence to help your organization win. We specialize in turning challenges into growth opportunities through immersive experiences that inspire and engage.

Ready to unlock your organization's full potential? 🔑

Partner with a team that knows how to win. We have a proven track record of delivering exceptional results, and we're excited to do it again—with you.

📧 Contact us: hello@talentx.global
🎙️ Get inspired: Tune in to our Future@Work podcast on Spotify, in collaboration with Letswork!
📍 Find us: Dubai 🇦🇪 | Riyadh 🇸🇦

name: Alex Zagrebelny
title: CEO & Owner
headline: Founder and CEO at R.Evolution
organization_short_description:
Why We Are Different
At R.Evolution, we believe that real estate is about more than just buildings—it's about creating spaces that resonate with the soul of a city, enriching the lives of its inhabitants. Unlike many who prioritize cost efficiency over quality and societal well-being, we craft each project with a purpose, ensuring that it embodies the values of comfort, harmony, and sustainability.

In a world where endless profit drives companies to cut corners and prioritize market dominance, we choose a different path. Our focus is not on how much more we can gain but on how much value we can create. From decoding architecture to final interior details, we design spaces that foster well-being, happiness, and a deeper connection to the present moment.

Our Mission
To create a universe of well-being filled with awareness and gratitude, joy and an opportunity for development and enhancement of longevity and potential of people and companies, using ancient knowledge of human nature, the latest achievements of the modern world and the highest level of sustainability

By the Numbers
• Largest single development: €270 million
• Total gross development value of projects: €500-600 million
• Expertise in residential, office, hotel, and infrastructure projects
• Headquartered in Dubai, with offices in Latvia, Spain, Germany, and the UAE

name: Mohammed Khan
title: Co-Founder & Ceo
headline: Co-founder & CEO - Dezzex & Dronex365  in Stealth mode, Solving challenging Problems in computer vision. #AI for inspection, #Technology Enabler for automotive industry, DroneAI Platform.
organization_short_description:
Dezzex Technologies is a cutting-edge Artificial Intelligence company that specializes in facilitating the seamless adoption of AI-driven solutions for growing businesses and government agencies. With a special focus on Smart Cities, Government functions, Policing, and Road Safety, we are on a mission to redefine the way cities operate and how safety measures are implemented across multiple sectors.

At the heart of our innovation is a proprietary AI platform built around Vision Transformer technology. This advanced AI system brings context to every frame of visual data it processes, thereby driving innovation in multiple areas. The result is smarter, safer cities where data-driven decisions can be made in real-time.
Features
• Context-Aware Analysis: Provides nuanced understanding of scenes and activities.
• Real-Time Processing: Capable of analyzing computer vision large streams of data in real-time.
• Scalable: Can be adapted for various industries and applications.
Smart Accident Reporting
We are proud to collaborate with the Dubai Police to implement our Smart Accident Reporting solution. This innovative system automates the process of accident reporting, saving time for both law enforcement agencies and citizens. Through AI-powered analytics, the system can quickly assess accident scenes and generate detailed reports, thereby expediting the resolution process.
Drone Imagery Analysis
Our AI platform specializes in drone imagery analysis, unlocking a wealth of use cases across sectors. Whether it's for urban planning, emergency response, or infrastructure maintenance, our system provides invaluable insights that can transform operations and improve efficiency.
Industries
We Serve: Government agencies, Smart cities projects, Drone operator, Drone service providers, Drone Manaufacturer, Telecom tower operators, check out our platform : www.dezzex.com & www.dronex365.com.

name: Artur Vlasov
title: CEO & Founder
headline: CEO & Founder – AVS Shipbrokers LLC
organization_short_description:
AV Shipbrokers is a shipbroker firm specializes at commercial ship management and dry cargo chartering. 

The company is established in 2020 and has already proven to be reliable broker and partner for continuous business relations both to charterers and shipowners.

We fix vessels for shipping following cargoes:
Coal
Grain
Agricultural products
Fertilizers
Break bulk cargoes

Our company works with following types of vessels:
Сoasters of DWAT 1 500-10 000 mt
Handysizes of DWAT 10 000 mt - 30 000 mt
Handymaxes of DWAT 30 000 mt - 60 000 mt
Panamaxes of DWAT 60 000 mt - 82 000 mt

During 2022, we shipped about 120 000 mt of grain in Mediterranean Sea, 50 000 mt of fertilizers in Persian Gulf, Red Sea and Mediterranean Sea and made about 39 fixtures of break bulk cargo including industrial assets, specialized and commercial machinery, bagged cargoes and other part cargoes in different trading areas.

On all enquiries please feel free to contact us on e-mail: info@avshipbrokers.com

name: Ankit Baradia
title: Founder/CEO
headline: Founder & CEO at CURD - The World’s 1st Social Search Engine | Transforming Networks into Revenue | Leveraging AI to Elevate Searches with Social Validation | Empowering Users and Businesses to Monetize Connections
organization_short_description:
CURD is an AI-powered Worlds 1st Social search engine that connects social media with search engine to help you Monetize your network like never before –
1. Earn Money By Promoting Businesses You Trust
2. Seek Referrals From Your Network For Any Requirement
3. Find Social Validation For Every Search From People You Trust
4. Transform Your Network Into The Powerhouse For Lead Generation

PROMOTE BUSINESSES AND EARN MONEY
Have you ever thought that engaging with your network could actually make you money? It's true.

How it works:
1. Sign Up & Acquire Your Network: Sign up to CURD and connect your social media profiles to quickly build your network. We understand how challenging it can be to start from scratch.

2. Refer To Earn Twice: You can make a referral and get rewarded by the businesses for promoting them. And if there is a business closure, you also earn a percentage of the deal value.

3. Collaborate To Earn: You can collaborate with businesses on CURD and earn money from your social media posts based on views, likes, and comments.

4. Instant Cashout: When a business rewards you, funds are instantly credited to your CURD wallet as CURD coins. These can be cashed out by transferring them to your bank account.

PERSONALIZED AND ORGANIC SEARCH RESULTS: We offer organic, non-sponsored and socially validated search results personalized by our AI, which considers the preferences and engagement of each person in your network using over 30 parameters to rank the results. 

TRUSTED REVIEWS AND RATINGS: Access credible reviews from your network, building trust and authenticity in your choices

GET REFERRALS: Create referral requests and gather referrals from your network. You can also search for products or services with confidence, thanks to social validation—all in one convenient place.

GENERATE ORGANIC LEADS FOR YOUR BUSINESS THROUGH ROBUST SEARCH RESULTS, WORD-OF-MOUTH AND AI MATCHMAKING

DOWNLOAD CURD FROM APPSTORE AND PLAYSTORE NOW!

name: Anas Albayari
title: Founder and CEO
headline: Founder and CEO Krave | Managing Director Apex Travels
organization_short_description:
Krave is a healthy restaurant concept, founded with the aim of serving quality tasty healthy changing the perception of healthy food by normalizing it through making delicious healthy food recipes with high quality premium ingredients, in a fun restaurant environment and approach to make healthy eating more desirable.

The stereotype of eating healthy has been always linked to eating salads and tasteless food that people feel forced to eat to maintain a healthy lifestyle. Krave concept is changing that by serving the delicious popular food people like in a healthy way using the finest healthy ingredients. 

Krave embraces the importance of eating healthy food as a part of a healthy lifestyle, which leads to create healthier future for the people.

Krave serves Healthy Food, Fresh Juices, Single Origin Coffee, and Light Desserts. There are varieties for Vegans, and Vegetarian as well as gluten-free and other nutrition preferences.

name: Vishal Mann
title: Founder and CEO
headline: Founder and CEO | Enterprise ICT Solutions Consultant | Technology Strategy & Sales
organization_short_description:
At Live in the Cloud (LITC), our commitment to excellence and innovation has earned us a distinguished reputation as a trusted partner for businesses seeking unparalleled IT solutions & services. With a dynamic team of seasoned professionals, we leverage over two decades of collective experience to deliver cutting-edge technologies that drive growth & efficiency.

As a leading IT value-added reseller (VAR) & Managed Service Provider (MSP), our primary focus is to empower businesses by streamlining their IT operations. We take pride in our ability to provide comprehensive support throughout the entire IT lifecycle, from the initial procurement of hardware & software to seamless integration and ongoing management of network infrastructure.

At the core of our mission lies a strong dedication to cybersecurity. As a Managed Security Service Provider (MSSP), we take a proactive approach to safeguarding our clients' sensitive data. Our team of security experts is vigilant in monitoring potential threats, ensuring early detection, and orchestrating swift incident responses to keep your digital assets protected.

We understand that each business is unique, which is why our IT solutions are tailored to meet specific industry needs & challenges. Our consultative approach ensures that we gain a thorough understanding of your business goals & pain points, enabling us to design bespoke IT strategies that drive meaningful outcomes.

Beyond our technical expertise, what truly sets us apart is our unwavering commitment to exceptional customer service. We prioritise building lasting relationships with our clients, and our dedicated team is always just a call away, ready to assist.

Partner with Live in the Cloud, and experience peace of mind that comes from having a reliable, forward-thinking IT partner by your side. Let us navigate the complexities of the digital landscape for you, so you can focus on what matters most: driving your business forward with confidence & success.

title: Founder & CEO
headline: Founder & CEO @ Madenat Al Nokhba Recycling Services L.L.C and Madenat Football Club
organization_name: Madenat Al Nokhba Recycling Services L.L.C
organization_short_description:
Vision: To inspire and encourage human race recover and reuse its resources.

Mission: To develop recycling solutions that continuously bring value to our customer's growing expectations.

Madenat Al Nokhba Recycling Services LLC. is the leading recycling entity located in the of heart of Jebel Ali, Dubai. We offer complete recycling solutions across various industries throughout the United Arab Emirates. With over 30 years' experience and expertise in e-waste & universal waste management, we provide tailor-made solutions for effective and efficient  waste management which are and we also commit to creating a safe and Eco-friendly atmosphere.

We at Madenat are aiming to support individuals and companies recover value of their used resources and increase market visibility through CSR initiatives. As a Dubai Municipality approved company we guarantee safe disposal of waste materials and we provide our customers with a Destruction/Recycling Certificate.

Our value-added services are tailored to cater business needs and center around below competencies:
      •	Technology: A fully fledged factory equipped with modern machinery that segregates & destructs the items to avoid disposal to landfill. Hence, ending the item's life cycle. 
      •	Comprehensive Solution: We eliminate the need of other service providers as our team can handle the safe collection and delivery of items in compliance with Dubai Municipality & global best practices. 
      •	Experience: We have established relationship with governing authorities to get proper documentation in timely manner.

name: Daniel Ahmed
title: Co-founder & Chief Operating Officer
headline: Building Fasset
organization_short_description:
Redefine the way money works for you, with Fasset. 

Fasset lets you seamlessly and securely manage all of your digital and real-world financial assets - from wherever you are, in your currency of choice. We believe in democratizing access to global assets, and that everyone, everywhere should be able to use their hard-earned money to buy high-quality, globally-traded assets to build and preserve their wealth. 

Through Fasset, you can: 
⚫ Invest in both digital as well as real-world assets like stocks, bonds, commodities and precious metals.
⚫ Tap into our trading platform and take advantage of a wide range of tokenized assets, including real-time market data.
⚫ Connect to a digital wallet that makes shopping and transferring funds user-friendly, with integrated payment solutions for easy conversion.
⚫ Transfer or receive funds securely and conveniently from wherever you are worldwide with the Fasset Connect Network. 

The security of our customers' funds, data and earnings are our top priority. 

We are regulated by the Virtual Assets Regulatory Authority (VARA). 

No aspect of this platform is intended to provide, or should be interpreted as providing, any investment, tax, legal, financial, or other advice of any kind. The materials presented on this platform should not be considered a substitute for professional advice. If you decide to engage in transactions based on any material found on this platform, the decisions, transactions, and any consequences that arise are solely your responsibility. While other users may share investment advice or opinions, please be aware that such advice or opinions are merely conversational exchanges between individuals who may be anonymous or unidentifiable. Fasset explicitly does not provide investment advice directly, indirectly, implicitly, or in any manner whatsoever. It is recommended that you use any information obtained from this platform as a starting point for your own independent research.

name: Marc Cirera
title: Founder and CEO
headline: Founder of Companies for Good
organization_short_description:
We are making this world a better place. 

Lots of companies in the UAE want to make a positive contribution to the community. They want to engage with colleagues, because they know that enhances collaboration and productivity. And they want to use Corporate Social Responsibility to do good – they know how important it is, they know society expects it of businesses, and they know that the UAE government has declared 2017 as "The Year of Giving". 

The problem is that many companies don't know what to do or how to do it. 

Companies for Good is here to help. We make it easy for you to make a positive impact – on your employees and society. 

At Companies for Good, we help businesses organise successful team-building activities, support their communities, protect the planet and make their organisations more sustainable. All our initiatives are designed to engage teams – and boost wellbeing and happiness for everyone involved.

Help the UAE promote the spirit of giving. Become a Company For Good.

name: Ivan Golov
title: CEO & Founder
headline: Founder at Shopobill - retail media gamification & sales incentive programs
organization_short_description:
Shopobill is a Retail Media and Shopper Engagement solution that helps retailers and FMCG/CPG producers to grow sales. 

- Self service system for retailers to launch and promote value added promotions on behalf of FMCG producers
- No code promotion engine with 400+ tested & proven mechanics to stimulate FMCG goods off-take in retail store (offline & e-com)
- Purchased based media targeting solutions to promote value based promotion offers and attract new customers to retail stores

SAAS no-code platform that helps to quickly prepare and efficiently run consumer activation campaigns, with mechanics like buy&get, instant win, cashback, participate in a prize draw, scan&win, spin the wheel, and much more. 

Shopobill platform includes: 

- Web builder for website and chatbots with participant personal account
- 400+ promo mechanics
- OCR validation 
- Automated prize draw 
- Digital prizes distribution 
- Newsletters and notifications for users
- Real-time promotion dashboards

Henkel, Ehrmann, Abbott, Mastercard, Coty, and Puig use Shopobill to automate their consumer promotion.  

Our customers have run over 1000 successful promotions impacting  millions of  shoppers. 

Sign up for a free consultation & demo on our website!

name: Avramis Despotis
title: Founder & CEO
headline: Tradepedia Ltd
organization_short_description:
Tradepedia is a leading provider of educational seminars and workshops to institutional and retail traders across the Middle East, North Africa, Asia and Europe. Founded by renowned financial analyst and risk management expert, Avramis Despotis, Tradepedia has built a portfolio of clients that represent some of the world's leading banking and financial institutions.

Using a practical, hands-on approach, their highly qualified trainers provide clients with a solid basis in technical analysis, risk management and behavioural finance in multiple languages. Trading excellence is nurtured by equipping clients with the knowledge, strategies and tools to become self-sufficient for long-term financial gain.

More than a training institute, Tradepedia has developed a series of intuitive market tools that enable traders to conduct complex and time-consuming analyses in a matter of minutes. Tradepedia proprietary tools for Metatrader, Zag Trader and Metastock enable traders to identify high-potential trade opportunities and place assured and timely trades.

Tradepedia's Avramis Despotis, is an enthusiastic educator and authoritative voice in price action trading. He has been involved in the financial markets for over two decades and has mentored thousands of private and institutional traders. His technical analysis reports and signals are sought after by clients and stock brokers around the world.

Avramis adds, "Our vision is to help traders make educated trading decisions and to gain financial independence. We believe that successful traders need a deeper understanding of the global financial markets and inter-market relationships to minimise risk and maximise potential return of investment".

Through its popular workshops and in-demand market software, Tradepedia has evolved into one of the foremost training institutes in the region. Licenced in Dubai by the DIFC with licence no. CL1433, we adhere to the highest professional and ethical standards.

title: Changing employee behaviour and mindset with an innovative digital learning solution - Guaranteed ➤ COO
headline: Changing employee behaviour and mindset with an innovative digital learning solution - Guaranteed ➤ COO @Habiiit
organization_short_description:
NoMoreCourses challenges what's not working in modern-day learning and education. We bring thought leadership and innovative products and services together in our quest to shape the future of talent development.

What are the options available to you? Another course on Workplace Safety, another day away from your staff's workstation to learn more on Customer Service? 

Not anymore, now you can change your team's behaviour whilst at work, simply by using the Habiiit Application on their mobile devices. No more lecturers, no more trainers, no more training venues and no more time away from work.

Habiiit uses micro learning campaigns focusing on your specific business' pain points with the aim to successfully effect behaviour change so you can see the measured improvement of what really matters - your bottom line.

Since its founding in 2019, PARFUMERY has rapidly established itself as the premier provider of bespoke perfumes and experiences for luxury brands such as Jaeger Le-Coultre, corporations such as Pfizer, and several high-net-worth individuals.

name: Donatas Varnas
title: Co-Founder & COO
headline: Co-founder & COO - ECOBLOX | HPC | AI Data Centers | Hardware | Computing
organization_short_description:
ECOBLOX is powering the modular future of supercomputing. We offer an innovative "Ecosystem of Blocks", a flexible turnkey solution that provides customers everything required for High Performance Computing (HPC) and Artificial Intelligence (AI). From planning, designing, building, optimizing and supporting, our modular full-stack data centers are scalable and sustainable. We enable our customers to get to market quickly and cost efficiently. And we don't stop there.

With cutting-edge designs for cooling, efficiency and density, the infrastructure we build is among the greenest in the world, demonstrating our commitment to sustainability and energy efficiency. We help our customers meet increasingly stringent sustainability regulations to reduce carbon footprint while still enjoying the high performance, low cost, and energy efficient computing power they need.
 
ECO-system - strong supply chain relationships ensure state-of-the-art solutions at the best price.
ECO-nomical - end-to-end support and ongoing optimization lowers costs and risk.
ECO-friendly -  we design, build and recycle with the environment in mind.

name: Raman Pathak
title: Co-Founder & CEO
headline: Building GCC's fastest "Fast Mile Delivery Network"
organization_short_description:
We are a tech-driven logistics solution brand delivering joy to our partners as well as individuals, empowering them to seamlessly manage their business and personal shipments, respectively.

We are proud to set new standards with ‘Last Mile Logistics 2.0' introducing Fast Mile Logistics. Realizing the shift in industry trend from 3-4 days delivery time to same day delivery, our version 2.0 fast tracks and optimises the entire fullfilment process.

The company is growing at an extraordinary pace from 0.1 million orders successfully delivered in 2017 to more than 20+ million orders. With the current growth, the founders and team have a clear road map to expand the footprint across GCC and other potential markets.

ConvexSol is your trusted partner for comprehensive IT solutions and strategic consulting, empowering businesses in the heart of the Middle East to thrive in this digital era. Our team of passionate professionals combines deep industry knowledge with a relentless drive for innovation, crafting solutions tailored for your unique needs.

We are your one-stop IT shop offering comprehensive suite of tailor-made software, robust infrastructure, & seamless cloud adoption:

1. Web & Mobile App Development: Engage your audience and enhance user experience with custom web and mobile app

2. Software Development: Streamline operations and empower your workforce with bespoke HR apps, enterprise solutions, and SAP HRMS implementation expertise.

3. Infrastructure & Security: Smooth IT operations and robust security with expert management and cutting-edge solutions.

4. Digital Transformation: Navigate the digital landscape seamlessly with our strategic guidance and cloud adoption expertise.

5. Data & AI: Gain data-driven insights and harness AI/ML to optimize operations, make informed decisions, and gain a competitive edge.

6. E-commerce & UI/UX: Create a seamless and engaging online shopping experience with our e-commerce solutions and user-centric design.

7. Testing & QA: Ensure the quality and performance of your applications and systems with rigorous processes.

From sales growth to team empowerment and future security, meet the ConvexSol product suite:

-> ConvexVzit - Secure your environment with visitor access control, automated notifications, and comprehensive security measures.

-> ConvexHR - Providing self-service portals, performance management tools, and seamless payroll, fostering a thriving workforce.

-> ConvexCRM - Leveraging AI to boost conversion rates, personalize outreach, and deliver real-time insights.


Connect with us today and unlock the full potential of your IT landscape. Together, let's shape the future of your business and go the extra mile.

organization_short_description:
Tereza Estates is a dynamic boutique real estate brokerage offering an exceptional tailored approach and superior customer service as well as unique access to some of our off market luxury lifestyle home opportunities.

Connecting sellers and buyers, both locally as well as internationally we strive to meet the diverse needs of our international client base with our creative and diligent approach as well as undeniable passion for the luxury real estate market in the most vibrant and fastest growing city in the world that continuously succeeds in impressing all of us  - Dubai.

Tereza Estates is led by The Founder & CEO Tereza, who has chosen to have her own name in the company brand, as hallmark of integrity, quality and transparency with aim to create an experience for our clients, where the company owner is reachable to talk to whether you are planning to purchase your very first property or you already are an experienced real estate veteran.
                                                                                                                                      Tereza brings with her an extensive real estate experience of over a decade in the real estate market of Dubai, as well as having previously collaborated with other real estate partners in multiple locations across the world to provide global solutions of real estate advisory and possibly expand to other countries across the globe in the future.

Home changes everything and we know. Therefore, let us help you to find the perfect place to call your own!

organization_short_description:
We believe every individual should have the opportunity to realise their potential.

We believe in unlocking potential at individual, team, management, leadership and organisational levels.

We believe that when the right people are in the right roles and given the right support, individuals grow, organisations succeed and communities flourish.

We build high-success, high-empathy, high-quality Leadership Teams.  We build high-performing, capable, engaging and efficient management teams.  And we build high-performance cultures and engaged workforces.  

We create great places to work.

Our solutions are norm-challenging, impactful, energetic and experiential, and suit companies of all sizes, anywhere in the world.  

We are honored to have served the likes of Microsoft, McKinsey, Merrill Lynch, DAMAC Properties, PwC, BCG, Accenture, Honeywell, EY, Philips, GfK-Nielsen, Etisalat, in markets including the US, LATAM, Europe, the Middle East and Asia.

And finally, we give 10% of all our revenue to the Melius Foundation so we can serve causes important to us as a team.  We are more than a for-profit business; we are an ethical business that cares about what we do and the world we live in.  

Welcome to Melius Consulting.  Welcome to #hrexcellence

HR Consulting | Leadership | Talent | Recruitment | Staffing | Learning | Coaching

name: Abdul Waris
title: Founder & CEO
headline: Founder & CEO
organization_short_description:
BitAffix is a cloud-based business process management platform that helps organizations streamline their workflows and improve their operational efficiency. With BitAffix, businesses can easily design, automate, and monitor their processes, enabling them to optimize their resources and focus on delivering value to their customers. Our user-friendly interface and flexible customization options make it easy for teams to collaborate and automate their processes, regardless of their industry or size.

BitAffix equips businesses from around the world with a comprehensive AI automation platform to revolutionize their digital transformation. With simple, low-effort solutions and unparalleled security, BitAffix is empowering companies of all sizes and industries on an end-to-end journey towards smart business process optimization.

Some key features of BitAffix include:

1. Customizable Workflows- BitAffix allows users to design and customize workflows specific to their business needs, making their operations more efficient and streamlined.

2. Data Capture and Management- The platform enables businesses to capture and manage data from various sources, such as forms, emails, and files, making it easier to keep track of information and make informed decisions.

3. Reporting and Analytics- BitAffix offers detailed reporting and analytics capabilities, allowing users to visualize and analyze their data to gain insights and improve their business operations.

4. Collaboration Tools - With BitAffix, teams can collaborate and communicate on tasks and projects in real-time, increasing productivity and transparency.

5. User Permissions and Security- The platform offers various user permissions and security features, ensuring that only authorized personnel have access to sensitive information and critical workflows.

6. Integration and Automation- Integrate with other tools and platforms, such as CRMs, ERPs, messaging apps & automate routine tasks, reducing manual effort & error.

name: Teresa Geneloni
title: Co-Founder, CEO
headline: Co-Founder TAF HOUSE MATERIAL in Dubai
organization_short_description:
At TAF House Material, our mission is to transform both interior and exterior spaces with designs that captivate physically, emotionally, and visually. Rooted in the rich heritage of Italian creativity and finely tuned to Middle Eastern architectural trends, we specialize in providing high-quality Italian porcelain tiles and wood flooring. Our expertise extends beyond just supplying materials; we collaborate closely with clients from concept to post-installation, ensuring complete satisfaction with sustainable and technically superior products.

Your Premier Tile Supplier in Dubai
We are proud to be one of the leading tile suppliers in Dubai, offering a diverse range of products including:

	•	Sanitary ware
	•	Wood Flooring
	•	Ceramic tiles
	•	Taps
	•	Custom carpets
	•	Terracotta tiles

All our materials are sourced directly from Italy and are made to the highest standards of Italian craftsmanship.

A Hub of Innovation and Timeless Style
Visit our showroom, a vibrant hub where trends, innovation, and timeless style in materials converge to inspire and fulfill your design visions. We believe that exceptional design is the foundation of beauty and our offerings reflect this philosophy. Our products represent the pinnacle of Italian design, seamlessly integrated with the latest architectural movements and design scenes in the Middle East.

Supporting Designers with Top-Quality Materials
As specialists in decorative Italian-made porcelain tiles and wood flooring, we supply materials from multiple esteemed brands dedicated to the Middle Eastern market. Our commitment to excellence ensures that designers and clients alike receive the best in quality and design.

Discover how TAF House Material can elevate your spaces. Visit us today and let us help bring your design dreams to life with our premium Italian-made products.

name: Pir Arkam
title: Founder & CEO
headline: Founder & CEO at Proto21
organization_short_description:
Proto21 3D Printing LLC, UAE, Dubai is formed in response to the burgeoning demand of the century's requirements on 3D Printing services and consultation. To become leading Additive Manufacturer in the region, Proto21 is partnered with Joseph Group of companies. Located in the industrial hub of Dubai, we aim to serve "Dubai 3D Printing Strategy", launched by His Highness Sheikh Mohammad bin Rashid Al Maktoum.

We are dedicated to accelerate the 3D printing adoption by providing Rapid Prototyping services with free consultation and delivering 3D printing training workshops. Proto21 3D Printing LLC has a solution for every phase of the product development cycle in all of the major industries.

We just don't 3D Print or 3D Model, we can make the concepts in your mind into reality, from the very scratch. We provide a dedicated professional for each project which serves you full consultation throughout the process for the design, functionality, finishes, choosing different materials, 3D printing or traditional manufacturing technologies, low volume production to high volume production and also towards the business point of view. 

With skills, technology and mastery of the 3D printing technology, our business and customer services are here to help you to achieve great projects.
